channel.title: Biggest profit/ loss
channel.description: Post your biggest profit or loss for ANYTHİNG İN RS. Today, i made 30m merching :D then i got greedy and bet 90m in flower game :/

item.title: Biggest profit/ loss
item.dc:creator: @Kidpaparoach Kidpaparoach
item.description:
@Kidpaparoach wrote:

Started at about 98m with dicing in cash, wanted to make it a nice round figure and I had discovered sniping(dicing days) got all the way up to 700m. Yes, 700m cash stack. Was going for divine + enough money for some nice shizz but slowly kept going down till was at about 400m and I was stupid and went and did a 400m bet with the last of my cash stack = gf it all.
After that my biggest loss would’ve been 250m from the flower game like 2-3months ago. Stopped betting for the most part, make so much more of a loss from my cockiness than a profit.
In my opinion, biggest profit would be the fire cape. When I got it not many people bought them so I was like yeyeyyeye woooooo. Sentimental value at the time, made me feel pro so in my opinion thats my biggest profit. Its defo smexier than my tokhaar by far.
